WHEREAS, Dr. Coreil's lifetime of leadership and service has been recognized
through his induction into the LSU AgCenter Hall of Fame, the Louisiana 4-H Hall of Fame,
the National 4-H Hall of Fame, and the Louisiana Agriculture Hall of Distinction; and
WHEREAS, Dr. Coreil's legacy is one of stewardship, bold vision, educational
access, workforce development, youth advancement, and faithful service to the state of
Louisiana.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
commend and honor Dr. Paul Dean Coreil on the occasion of his retirement as Chancellor
of Louisiana State University of Alexandria and does recognize his many accomplishments
and lasting contributions to higher education, public service, youth development, and the
people of Louisiana.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby express
its deepest appreciation to Dr. Paul Dean Coreil for his decades of dedicated leadership and
service and extends best wishes to him in his retirement.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Dr.
Paul Dean Coreil.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
SPEAKER OF THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
